
BRANDING
============================================================

Thegithir-branded pages:

   o  /
      Home page

   o  /boards
      list of all boards

   o  /user-boards
      list of boards owned by the signed-on user

   o  /user-posts
      list of posts owned by the signed-on user

Board-branded pages:

   o  /board

   o  /board?id=

   o  /edit-board

   o  /edit-board?id=

   o  /edit-post


ACCESSIBILITY
============================================================

Pages accessible to everyone:

   o  /
      Home page

   o  /board?id=

Pages accessible only to signed-on users:

   o  /edit-board
      Create a new board

   o  /edit-post
      Create a new post on a board

Pages accessible only to the owner:

   o  /user-boards
      list of boards owned by the signed-on user

   o  /user-posts
      list of posts owned by the signed-on user

   o  /edit-board?id=
      Edit an existing board

Pages accessible only to the administrator:

   o  /boards
      A listing of all boards


SCREEN SIZES
============================================================

   240x320  Android entry level
   320x480  Android mid level
   480x800  Andriod high-end;  Windows Phone 7
   640x960  iPhone 4 "retina
   720x1280 Android next-gen
   800x1200 Galaxy Note
